  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening Capacities for Crisis Assessment and Recovery Planning</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of the project is to assist national and regional stakeholders to improve their abilities to prepare, assess, plan, implement and sustain recovery and peacebuilding activities. This will be achieved through i) increasing institutionalization and adaptation of the PDNA and DRF methodologies  to the national and regional context; ii) supporting capacity-building efforts to facilitate assessment processes and systematic follow up; iii) Rolling out the RPBA methodology.</narrative>
  </description>
